   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Views from the Frontline 2013 (VFL 2013)  &#x2013; Armenia and Georgia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Oxfam alongside its partner Regional Environmental Centre (REC) Caucasus will implement in Georgia and Armenia Views from the Frontline 2013, an initiative of the Global Network of Civil Society Organizations for Disaster Reduction (GNDR). Views from the Frontline is an alternative survey of progress towards implementation of the Hyogo Framework for Action, focusing on achievements in disaster risk reduction (DRR) at the local level. Recommendations are used at the national and global levels to foster improved DRR governance.</narrative>
